{"tid":708392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警協會新主席：叫「黑警」者寥寥可數","createTime":"2018-06-19T09:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T00:44:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f272961d5543fd51d2b17f8d0e47299d76ac2d","tid":708392,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529392574_0379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529392574_0379.jpg&h=397be3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察隊員佐級協會早前改選，隸屬港島總區、衝鋒隊警署警長林志偉接替陳祖光任主席，就職禮今日舉行。林志偉接受《星島》訪問時表示，警察執法時絕對政治中立，「不理建制、民主派，有任何人犯法，我們就執法」，但他認為收工後警察有思想自由，區會或立會選舉時協會出通告提醒會員投票，只是呼籲支持與協會理念相同的人。林志偉認為大部分市民理性守法，好支持警隊，稱警察為「黑警」的人寥寥可數，衷心希望「社會風氣唔好再壞落去」。<br />\n<br />\n去年2月，警察員佐級協會等多個協會舉行特別會員大會，表達對七警案判刑的不滿，並要求設立保護公職人員免受侮辱的條例，有逾3萬人出席。席間台上發言者大喊「X你老母」，台下大批集會者和應。林志偉在訪問中重申，只要觸及警察權益，一定會爭取，發聲只為捍衛警察的尊嚴和地位，如再有事件觸碰警察尊嚴底線，不排除再來。<br />\n<br />\n警察隊員佐級協會有約2.3萬名會員、佔整體警隊員佐級人員88%，林志偉指，就辱警罪、侮辱公職人員罪立法是必須的，「有些人士故意挑釁、攻擊，要用法例管制」，但不是「講句粗口就侮辱你，就拉得」，因執法都要蒐證，如突然好激氣、非刻意挑釁講幾句粗口，「尚可以容忍」。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉認為，現時警民關係並非惡劣，盼市民明白並尊重警方執法者的角色。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180619/58335743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58335743&d=kfGbL%2FOjNJwp4oeQaGZtP9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7e15ce59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58335743&h=f44c1800\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180619/58335743</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a4a1dddcdef38f4edda44b175ee82c4d70f0b6","tid":708392,"uid":54502,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"叫開警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9344d15f004b81cb7442dce551388c4b36a035d","tid":708392,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46a4a1dddcdef38f4edda44b175ee82c4d70f0b6","tid":708392,"uid":54502,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"叫開警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3f6c660577992093db5507081f749ea2abe027","tid":708392,"uid":146535,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"至弊叫你警察都唔見得係尊重你"},{"pid":"46ab16fc8b652f3b45783355ee3722291f44e3ea","tid":708392,"uid":33789,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"叫開黑警犬"},{"pid":"76762450b0354272de72af9800ce3a6ae84d4033","tid":708392,"uid":10433,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"休班警&gt;黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33d1cd5ad8f857c544e895a2f07585030472dd5","tid":708392,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"真係黑 人問號"},{"pid":"9dd3272bda6d3660fb7122f60d9b1c24471b494d","tid":708392,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"慈母"},{"pid":"19f23543fdf9593b15cda40673eaadf840069be5","tid":708392,"uid":59283,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"叫開警渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d8d5c6ab8c92a6f8a5dc8b9835450d467f2379","tid":708392,"uid":2545,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"r